Steve> perfectly understandable. If it were possible to link notice
Steve> boards in SW to the mailing lists, so that everything that
Steve> appeared on the notice boards would also appeal on the mailing
Steve> lists, would some of your concerns be met?

Not really.  The Nomic World experience has demonstrated that
attempting to implement Rule-defined structures within automation is a
bad idea.  I prefer the relatively lack of dependence on automation
that we have now and am loathe to surrender that for the dubious and
unproved merits of moving onto a MUD.

